^ DK (3 August 2009). 1000 CEOs. Dorling Kindersley Limited. p. 137. ISBN 978-1-4053-5272-7. 
^ "Daniel DiMicco, 2006 Steelmaker of the Year" (PDF). Retrieved 12 November 2016. 
